ActAccess to Information Act
PrecisAppointment of CAROLINE MAYNARD of Ottawa, Ontario, to be the interim Privacy Commissioner, to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending on October 31, 2022, or until such time as a new Privacy Commissioner is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective June 4, 2022.
